description: Another friday arrived. I bet you are as exhausted as I am after work week. To cheer you up a bit I went out with my cam again to help solve some money issues. I already visited 64 habitats usually vacated with young moneyless dudes with some kind of brain malfunction. I always wonder how come they are so stupid that they spend so much more than they earn. Every day I receive more than 20 email or calls, asking for help. And I always help. If they somehow attract me. This young pal was no different than the others. In debts, owing money to family, friends and of course bank. I don’t really get it, really. I was in a mood for a long and tasty blow job. So I asked for it, and he didn’t have any other chance.
title: Debt Dandy 64
